	<table class="table instructions-table">
		<tr><td>
			<div class="">
				<h1>Playing The Game</h1>
			</div>	
			<div class="textcenter">
				<p> 
					To begin, you’ll have a deck of cards containing some
					Exploding Kittens. You play the game by putting the
					deck face down and taking turns drawing cards off
					the top until someone draws an Exploding Kitten.
				</p>
